Swiss Bank Mergers to Continue, UBS’s Wiesendanger Tells L’Agefi

-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 
2011-12-09T07:05:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/swiss-bank-mergers-to-continue-ubs-s-wiesendanger-tells-l-agefi.html
Consolidation in Swiss banking will
continue, in particular among firms with international clients,
l’Agefi reported, citing an interview with Christian
Wiesendanger, the head of  UBS AG (UBSN) ’s Swiss wealth unit.  UBS is seeing more growth in private banking in Geneva and
the Romande region of  Switzerland  than in Zurich, Wiesendanger
told the Swiss newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Giles Broom in Geneva at 
 gbroom@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
